data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom oasis in the city of Murrieta with an inviting atmosphere and space for all of your needs.  Upon entering, you will be greeted with a spacious living room complete with cozy fireplace, a functional layout, and a spacious dining area.  The main floor also offers a convenient bedroom with bathroom, ideal for guests or as a flexible office space.  Adjacent to the kitchen, you will find that it opens up to the covered patio, providing a seamless indoor outdoor living experience.  Step outside and you will discover a backyard paradise that will beckon you to unwind and entertain with a sparkling pool and a relaxing spa to make the most of the California lifestyle.  This residence also offers the convenience of a dedicated laundry room and a generous 3-car garage with ample storage space.  This home is situated in a highly sought after neighborhood, offering tranquility and easy access to local amenities.  The spacious interior, outdoor haven, and thoughtful details, make this property a rare gem.  Do not miss the opportunity to make this exceptional home your own.
